import React from "react";
import {
  Box,
  Grid,
  Text,
  Flex,
  Accordion,
  Center,
  Avatar,
  Badge,
  Checkbox,
  Button,
  ColorPicker,
  Input,
  Stack,
  Image,
  Card,
  Slider,
  ActionIcon,
} from "@mantine/core";

const MostPopulerProduct = () => {
  return (
    <Accordion.Item value="most-populer-product">
          <Accordion.Control bg="indigo.2">
            <Center>
              <Text fw={700}>Most Populer Product</Text>
            </Center>
          </Accordion.Control>
          <Accordion.Panel>Content</Accordion.Panel>
        </Accordion.Item>
  )
}

export default MostPopulerProduct
